{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77550c23-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s410hh–3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"410hh–3"},"text":"§ 410hh–3.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Native selections","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Valid Native Corporation selections, or lands identified for selection by Regional Corporations pursuant to section 17(d)(2)(E) of the Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s1616/d/2/E"},"text":"43 U.S.C. 1616(d)(2)(E)","children":[],"tail":"], within the boundaries of the Wrangell-Saint Elias National Park and Preserve as established under this Act, are hereby recognized and shall be honored and conveyed by the Secretary in accordance with the Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s1601"},"text":"43 U.S.C. 1601","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] and this Act."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77550c24-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/487/tII/s204"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–487, title II, § 204","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-12-02"},"text":"Dec. 2, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2384"},"text":"94 Stat. 2384","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77575615-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77575616-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77575617-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/203"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–203","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1971-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 1971","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/85/688"},"text":"85 Stat. 688","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 33 (§ 1601 et seq.) of Title 43, Public Lands. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s1601"},"text":"section 1601 of Title 43","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/487"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–487","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-12-02"},"text":"Dec. 2, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2371"},"text":"94 Stat. 2371","children":[],"tail":", known as the Alaska National Interest Lands Conservation Act. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s3101"},"text":"section 3101 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
